{"tid":1750624,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北朗區選民 去撚左邊？","createTime":"2019-11-24T12:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T14:24:08.000Z","uid":153781,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ad9ec61a56ae14f360aaf8d286bba04bc04fea","tid":1750624,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191124&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60305192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191124%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60305192&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=0e830ab7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191124%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60305192&h=a96e101d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191124&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60305192</a><br />\n<br />\n曾在超級區議會憑49萬票膺「票王」的「鄺神」鄺俊宇，在今日區議會選舉選情卻出現大逆轉，晚上留守其出選的元朗北朗選區拉票，但至今情況非常不樂觀，無奈下要大打「告急牌」。鄺俊宇晚上接受《蘋果》訪問時直言「選戰陷入苦況」，全因北朗區投票率低，據他所知，北朗區有10,395名選民，惟截至下午6時半，累積投票率只有約54.53%，仍比全港60.36%低。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋面對一個強大嘅配票機器，如果投票率低對我哋選情非常不利！」現年36歲的鄺俊宇，於2007年首次參選區選，就成功當選，當時只有24歲。其後在北朗區連任3屆區議員，惟今年競逐連任卻出奇地嚴峻。他形容低投票率絕對是一個警號，建制派下午派出重量級人物如梁志祥等強攻，而低投票率令全元朗區民主派候選人選情緊張，他呼籲各位選民盡快出來投票，「千祈唔好睇小自己一票，多你一票真係多好多！」<br />\n<br />\n我哋真係唔係贏梗㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鄺俊宇係依幾個月咁出力 有咩可能會咁 北朗區唔好再係喺屋企喇 出到聲要輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快撚啲投票啦"},{"pid":"f829df703aac7dc4f3beaba6f8c3e19046b80f64","tid":1750624,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投資，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"79ac339c3dbaf94e50810179871470d1746d4a2a","tid":1750624,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e119649a5368b545c3930d2d1fbab4e185177376","tid":1750624,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"54.34% 大家瞓晒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2abd28f84583fcf09b3aa4c8d310d66c0c667a1","tid":1750624,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7694188771afca6613b23a9038c81dd60458d09c","tid":1750624,"uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:54:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1209247e82daaff27c54002628c634b02eff5b28","tid":1750624,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"北朗區選民